Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.70,0:00:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停下來呀
