Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不是喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不是愛我嗎！
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.82,標題,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}第二話　 回應我
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.23,0:00:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}早安…緒方
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.24,0:00:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊 早上好
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抱歉昨天 不能一起去
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}恩
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我跟美紀說了我有事去不了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.26,0:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想現在她們兩人應該在獨處吧
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無所謂
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒有什麼需要在意的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 美紀發生了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.75,0:00:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為 為什麼這麼問？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.21,0:01:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天晚上打電話過去了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.23,0:01:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}應該不舒服吧電話也沒接
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.35,0:01:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天她媽媽打電話說她今天不來上課了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 所以發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什 什麼也沒發生啊…
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.60,0:01:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哦..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但已經三天了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.34,0:01:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她一直呆在家裡,也不打電話給我
Dialogue: 2,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也許感冒了？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夏天感冒是很纏人的啦
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.39,0:01:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其實…我好像有點後悔了...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.39,0:01:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}後悔？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.21,0:01:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祭典我不該讓美紀一個人去
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.69,0:01:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我其實也想一起去
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和緒方一起去
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.04,0:01:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這樣的晚上我只能在我的房間看煙火
