Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.58,0:02:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要啊
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好痛…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要啊…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也許這就是戀愛吧
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不要開我玩笑了啦
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只是稍微想一下而已
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.82,0:02:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我最喜歡的還是A,W你啊
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我真的也想去看祭典
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和緒方一起
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現在美紀正和緒方
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看著煙花
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.33,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}突然內心好痛苦 嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什麼啊 我到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誰啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.03,0:02:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}來一下
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.42,0:03:06.17,等你,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在中庭等你來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:06.17,願望,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一生的願望{\r紅心}♥
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.95,0:03:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}真是的 一般情況下一生的願望會寫在紙飛機上嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}特地要我來這裡
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你一生的願望到底是什麼了啦
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要說的是…可以了…走吧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這怎麼行呢 特地為了衣里...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不過 這應該會給他造成困擾
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒事的啦
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要我請求的話 哥哥什麼都會聽
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}對吧！
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以是什麼啊那個願望
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.05,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是…衣里想要你做她的男朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哈...？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}衣里啊 一直被男的纏著很困擾
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}欸所以啊 衣里擁有哥哥這個男朋友的話
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那傢伙應該就會放棄了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是這樣的吧!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是..這樣...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一生的願望
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快幫助藍的摯友吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我說…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是這樣 求你了(この通り 行禮的意思)
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你覺得沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}文字測試而已啦
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聽你這麼說也確實是啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}澤永…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}緒方 快看快看 美紀...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.47,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}碧！再不快點的話圖書館要關了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}欸 啊 等下 美紀
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}澤永…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛苦了 美紀 我們先走了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛苦了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那 那個 可能你不想看到我的臉
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是 一會就好 我想請你聽我說
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.85,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}澤永？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我以前有個人渣父親
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為我帶有那個像怪物一樣的父親的血
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不會說什麼希望你原諒我的話
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}警察也好 把一切都曝光出去也好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.37,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是 至少想讓你知道我的歉意
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可以了 緒方
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我啊 那天晚上的事都已經忘了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請你也忘了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.51,0:05:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那個一定是事故
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.68,0:05:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}事故？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}對
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是事故
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.12,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只是我沒想到是那樣的初體驗
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是我…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你喜歡碧吧…
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你突然在說什麼？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就請你就去救碧
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}救她？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她其實沒什麼朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一個人的時候就會極端害怕
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}碧是出道的童星
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天就是 出演 出演
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.95,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為了減少出演頻率 碧就給父親寫信
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.85,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}信？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是那些信並沒有送到她父親手上
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.30,0:06:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}媽媽保管了那些信 回復則是經紀人写的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}瞞著碧本人 信上那些令人感動的話被出版成了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.88,0:06:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}著名童星與父親的愛和感動的書簡集
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她完全變成了別人商品化的道具
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}從那以後…
